    "The deliberate enactment is also considered moderate to ensure accurate predictions based on true requirements.",
    "Since most use cases occur in stable indoor environments, the sensitivity to the environment can be set to a low level.",
    "To enhance customer experience, minimizing user discomfort is prioritized, aiming for a low level of discomfort.",
